{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multi scrolling mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Seamlessly switching between side scroll, top-down, 3d shooter from behind and cut-scene. No camera cut during stage run. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Appearance</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No story narration. The story is abstract.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some parts of game are refered from other Touhou Project derivative works. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Characters are in alternate sexy costume<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/UtsuhoPanty_Version104Cropped_2_.png?t=1731862551\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Keyboard control (default)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arrow keys : Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">z : Shoot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">x : Use bomb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">c : Use special skill</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Left shift : Slowdown movement and aim at enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Space bar : turn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">escape : pause game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can set key config as you want in the option menu.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Playable characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hakurei Reimu<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/CharacterSelect_Reimu_Version104_360p.jpg?t=1731862551\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kirisame Marisa<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/CharacterSelect_Marisa_Version104_360p.jpg?t=1731862551\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Izayoi Sakuya<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/CharacterSelect_Sakuya_Version104_360p.jpg?t=1731862551\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Miscellaneous game play features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6 stages for main game + 1 extra stage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 difficulties. Easy, Normal and Hard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Screen resolution setting. 3840x2160, 3200x1800, 2560x1440, 1920x1080, 1280x720, 640x360. Choose which ever suitable for your machine. The game has better performance with a lower resolution. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cel-shade and Hitbox style setting. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/CelshadeAndHitboxSettings360p.png?t=1731862551\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hp and Mp regenerate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlimited continue. When player dies, player can continue at any unlocked checkpoint. If player use continue, the remaining hp is set to small amount.  No bad ending even a player use continue. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill enemies in close range to get more bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill enemies consecutively to get more chain bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Partially Japanese and Chinese translation. (Tutorial and UI)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Save game location</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">C:UsersusernameAppDataLocalTHMSS2</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Reimu Easy Clear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1480040/6b497c1e0778b054cc10ab931009c5aa07ad63fd.jpg"},{"name":"Reimu Normal clear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1480040/3cab47074653dc875b82192c2110963c09da95e8.jpg"},{"name":"Reimu Hard clear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pu